text:
generating a follow me module.

Basic jist I’m looping through a list of social networks, and looping through the account’s social icons that are  set in follow me settings.

networkName returns “facebook” or “twitter” etc

iconName is returning empty, nothing is getting stored whatsoever
```
  {% if module.use_social_settings %}
    {% for networkName in networks %}


      {%- set network = fm|selectattr('iconName','equalto',networkName)|last -%}

      {%- set imgURL = network.iconName ~'_legacy_color.png' -%}  
      {%- if network -%}
      &lt;!-- Network:{{network}}--&gt;
      &lt;!-- NetworkName:{{networkName}} --&gt;
          {% set iconName == "not being set" %}
          {% if networkName|string == "facebook" %}
            {% set iconName == "facebook-f" %}
          {% else %}
            {% set iconName == networkName %}
          {% endif %}&lt;!-- IconName:{{iconName}} --&gt;

        &lt;a href="{{ network.followMeUrl }}" {% if module.links %}target="_blank"{% endif %} class="fm_button fm_{{iconName}} " style="text-decoration: none"&gt;&lt;i class="fab fa-{{iconName}} fa-lg"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
      {%- endif -%}
    {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}
```
